></xhtml:br>3.3.3.11/4</tablecell><tablecell><link><target>Image:Antiprism 11-6.png</target><part>64px</part></link><xhtml:br></xhtml:br>3.3.3.11/6</tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablehead align="center">d<xhtml:sub>11d</xhtml:sub><xhtml:br></xhtml:br>[2<xhtml:sup>+</xhtml:sup>,11]<xhtml:br></xhtml:br>(2*11)</tablehead><tablecell><link><target>Image:Antiprism 11-3.png</target><part>64px</part></link><xhtml:br></xhtml:br>3.3.3.11/3</tablecell><tablecell><link><target>Image:Antiprism 11-5.png</target><part>64px</part></link><xhtml:br></xhtml:br>3.3.3.11/5</tablecell><tablecell><link><target>Image:Antiprism 11-7.png</target><part>64px</part></link><xhtml:br></xhtml:br>3.3.3.11/7</tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablehead align="center">d<xhtml:sub>12d</xhtml:sub><xhtml:br></xhtml:br>[2<xhtml:sup>+</xhtml:sup>,12]<xhtml:br></xhtml:br>(2*12)</tablehead><tablecell><link><target>Image:Antiprism 12-5.png</target><part>64px</part></link><xhtml:br></xhtml:br><link><target>Dodecagrammic antiprism</target><part>3.3.3.12/5</part></link></tablecell><tablecell><link><target>Image:Antiprism 12-7.png</target><part>64px</part></link><xhtml:br></xhtml:br><link><target>Dodecagrammic crossed-antiprism</target><part>3.3.3.12/7</part></link></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell>...</tablecell></tablerow></table><list type='bullet'><listitem><link><target>Prism (geometry)</target><part>Prism</part></link></listitem><listitem><link><target>Apeirogonal antiprism</target></link></listitem><listitem><link><target>Grand antiprism</target></link><space/>a four-dimensional polytope</listitem><listitem><link><target>One World Trade Center</target></link>, a building consisting primarily of an elongated square antiprism<extension extension_name='ref' name="Kabai2013"><template><target>cite web</target><arg name="last">Kabai</arg><arg name="first">Sándor</arg><arg name="title">One World Trade Center Antiprism</arg><arg name="url">http://demonstrations.wolfram.com/OneWorldTradeCenterAntiprism